column5: "Fishing is not a matter of life or death . It`s more important than that"
I saw a license plate frame last week that said "Women love me, fish fear me"
I saw a t-shirt that said "if fishing was easy it would be called 'your mom!'"   lol
I think someone here has that as their signature.
I apologize but it was new to me.
They are all good.  I like the one on the trailer the best.
Here's one that should definitely be a bumper sticker:  Bass are what you catch by accident while fishing for walleye!!!
This should keep things quiet during rush hour  " HONK IF YOU HAVE NEVER SEEN AN UZI FIRED FROM A CAR WINDOW "
that's been my signature line on this board for well over a year now.
I thought so. I just couldn't remember which one of you crusty son of a guns had it.
Here's one I've seen for all you Jeep and Toyota guys.lol  (I drive an FJ Cruiser)  "I know all about the Jeep thing......that's why I drive an FJ"
Or a new corvette I saw with a lovely young lady,and the license plate said WAS HIS ,nice eh!!!!
I wanted to make a sticker or Tee...."A day of Crappie fishing, is better than a good day at work"
or My wife said, "If I go fishing one more time she'll leave me' god I'm going to miss Her.
This place works great and the first one is cheap too. They did the shirt in my picture.  http://www.printfection.com/promo/two_dollar_tees.php?r=pf
Any day Fishing is better than any days work.
